{"tid":1858292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[武漢肺炎] 疫情影響交通 香港棺木面臨缺貨危機","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T15:53:42.000Z","uid":35070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63550d6ac1ad2f83b4eb2b7658b7419e452a06df","tid":1858292,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-02-02/361126?fbclid=IwAR1nI6RIyWs5fpG73PvSBwlyUeTukDgJAe2lS4-CPMu1uLz_WnPyH_uuFns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-02-02%2F361126%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1nI6RIyWs5fpG73PvSBwlyUeTukDgJAe2lS4-CPMu1uLz_WnPyH_uuFns&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=e1ed79db\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-02-02/361126?fbclid=IwAR1nI6RIyWs5fpG73PvSBwlyUeTukDgJAe2lS4-CPMu1uLz_WnPyH_uuFns</a><br />\n<br />\n受內地武漢肺炎疫情影響，許多地方封鎖交通不便，使得內地輸往香港的棺木供應大大減少，香港殯儀業商會發出的特別通告予殯儀業，指香港棺木供求緊張，只可維持供應到2月5日。為免引起棺木供應緊張，因此發出通告要求各殯儀業內人士向供應商訂購棺木時，提供火化收據證明以實名登記。<br />\n<br />\n香港殯儀業商會表示已去信向政府求助，殯儀業商會永遠會長吳耀棠表示，指發文通告的內容是邀請業界討論棺材緊張一事，也會聯絡供應商，或找政府幫忙，「不過政府連口罩都幫不到，怎幫買棺材？」吳耀棠表示，以往內地多個省市都有製作棺木的工廠，但因內地疫情嚴重，令交通嚴重受阻，再加上農曆新年假期剛完結，部分工人未及由鄉下回到工廠，因此導至棺木供不應求。<br />\n<br />\n香港食物環境衞生署表示，已在1月31日已收到商會的信件，因應內地疫情控制政策，廣東省主要棺木供應商至今未能復工生產供港棺木。政府已即時聯絡與內地當局作跟進，要求盡快協調批准在廣東省內的供應商復工復產，並盡快將現有存貨發運香港，緩解香港棺木貨量短缺的情況。<br />\n<br />\n至於因為大陸疫情嚴重，內地對棺木可能也是需求大增，是否導致內地會與香港「搶貨」，吳耀棠認為，各省市都有工廠製作棺木，相信不會有爭貨情况出現。他個人認為，如最後關頭找不到，可從東南亞入貨，稱當地都有華人會製造棺材，可以到該處找。"},{"pid":"e348f3a0d6fa94742121ad6001e6b0b2e5695a2c","tid":1858292,"uid":173598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"大陸用紙棺火化"},{"pid":"481b4417ad6712155057e3bca5266da097c9f5d2","tid":1858292,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e348f3a0d6fa94742121ad6001e6b0b2e5695a2c","tid":1858292,"uid":173598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"大陸用紙棺火化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"隨時紙棺都無貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d72b605dbf908e209a2603f10cb26df383f97d","tid":1858292,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d597d25556c518a0658dd944acf3766fe308bba1","tid":1858292,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"棺材本都可以慳番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bd88bc62c554c599c481e7bc9a845eabac71bb","tid":1858292,"uid":170297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"棺材都有得炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fedf5231f1c049c07380550814a1e4eb3b393b","tid":1858292,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"棺木期貨 口罩期貨"},{"pid":"917f66391ec0351759b473d3b5034ad101aa7c07","tid":1858292,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d597d25556c518a0658dd944acf3766fe308bba1","tid":1858292,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"棺材本都可以慳番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-nrt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/12047081_1488947294739299_154745145864527307_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ohc=AvAN365KC1cAX-F1-9p&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-nrt1-1.xx&amp;oh=f09c50c6f5c752c928a2eacf715dbf10&amp;oe=5EBCC8BE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-nrt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F12047081_1488947294739299_154745145864527307_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ohc%3DAvAN365KC1cAX-F1-9p%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-nrt1-1.xx%26oh%3Df09c50c6f5c752c928a2eacf715dbf10%26oe%3D5EBCC8BE&h=e4c02ae0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6335b8e03796461b88545e3ebf0ee55255b77b11","tid":1858292,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0bd88bc62c554c599c481e7bc9a845eabac71bb","tid":1858292,"uid":170297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"棺材都有得炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"搞搞下金銀衣紙都有得炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f098db0b73ec894a20ce2c27b1b597885eaab6e","tid":1858292,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"直接火化"},{"pid":"c9760a66175f0212ccd493fb881fbb619551b8a8","tid":1858292,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得之前財經台有人話福壽園係疫症概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}